<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Records of polydesmid species in Vietnam and of all known Pacidesmus species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976107" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Pacidesmus tuachua sp. nov., holotype ♂ (IEBR-Myr 951) A anterior part of body, dorsal view B anterior part of body, lateral view C anterior part of body, ventral view D segments 8 - 10, dorsal view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976115" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Pacidesmus tuachua sp. nov., holotype ♂ (IEBR-Myr 951) A segments 8 - 10, ventral view B-D posterior part of body, dorsal, vental and lateral views, respectively. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976116" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Pacidesmus tuachua sp. nov., holotype ♂ (IEBR-Myr 951) A telson, ventral view B telson, lateral view C right antenna, anterior view D gonopods in situ under UV light, ventral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976117" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Pacidesmus tuachua sp. nov., holotype ♂ (IEBR-Myr 951) A anterior part of body, under the UV light, dorsal view B segments 8 - 10, dorsal view C posterior part of body, dorsal view D posterior part of body, ventral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976118" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Pacidesmus tuachua sp. nov., holotype ♂ (IEBR-Myr 951) right gonopod, under UV light A mesal view B ventral view C lateral view D dorsal view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976119" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure14>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Pacidesmus tuachua sp. nov., holotype ♂ (IEBR-Myr 951) right gonopod A mesal view B lateral view. Abbreviations: co = coxite; pref = prefemorite; ca = cannula; en = endomere; pu = puvillus; p 1 = first process; p 2 = second process. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976120" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.114958.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Polydesmus vietnamicus Nguyen, 2009 from Ha Giang Province (IEBR-Myr 808) ♂, right gonopod A mesal view B lateral view. Abbreviations: co = coxite; pref = prefemorite; ca = cannula; en = endomere; sl = solenomere; mt = midway teeth; ap = additional process. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/976114" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

